metadata.name: Embracing the Citadel's Challenge
metadata.description:
Embracing the Citadel's Challenge, amidst a world full of distractions//

Drawing with my pen, away from all distractions, I find myself craving stimulation. Everything is within reach, but I understand that going through this is the only way forward. I hold an amethyst close to my heart, hoping it will heal me. And it did. It's the bit of hope that was needed//


Retake your power/  
Against all forces that try to take your attention/  
Intelligence has become purely intellectual/  
Escape the compulsive behavior/  
Escape the algorithms/  
Find out what you are doing/  
Develop the psychological strength/  
You might think that's impossible/  
But it's not impossible/  
Because people live through catastrophe/
